    "24) and its runtime performance advantage, allowing it to be run using CPU only (see Supplementary Table 1).",
    "More details on the computational considerations can be found in the Method section below.",
    "For all components, models perform better on the random set D2C-RND than on the uniform set D2C-UNI, confirming that documents published recently and in the United States are easier to automatically process.",
